article_id:1037,category_name:News,title_name:The First Round Of Limited-Time Packs Are Here!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8790e91173f1152c7ad760d3b90e43b4.png,message:<div>The Limited-Time Flame Upgrade Special, Limited-Time Light Upgrade Special, Limited-Time Champion&#39;s Pack, and Limited-Time Weapon Upgrade Special are available in the shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1580277600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1580277600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1581919199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Pack Details</div><div>1. Limited-Time Flame Upgrade Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading flame-attuned adventurers and facilities.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x2,400 (1,920 + 480 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Mana x200,000</div><div>・Knight&#39;s Testament x6</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x3</div><div>・Flame Orb x210</div><div>・Blaze Orb x70</div><div>・Inferno Orb x30</div><div>・Flamewyrm&#39;s Scale x150</div><div>・Flamewyrm&#39;s Scaldscale x50</div><div><br></div><div>2. Limited-Time Light Upgrade Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading light-attuned adventurers and facilities.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x2,400 (1,920 + 480 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Mana x200,000</div><div>・Knight&#39;s Testament x6</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x3</div><div>・Light Orb x210</div><div>・Radiance Orb x70</div><div>・Refulgence Orb x30</div><div>・Lightwyrm&#39;s Scale x150</div><div>・Lightwyrm&#39;s Glowscale x50</div><div><br></div><div>3. Limited-Time Champion&#39;s Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading adventurers and unlocking nodes on the mana circles.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x300 (192 + 108 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x1</div><div>・Gold Crystal x300</div><div>・Mana x75,000</div><div><br></div><div>4. Limited-Time Weapon Upgrade Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading weapons.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x1,230 (1,200 + 30 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Damascus Ingot x1</div><div>・Gold Whetstone x350</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Each limited-time pack may only be purchased once during the availability period.</div><div>2. For information about each pack, select the shop on the Home page, and see Limited-Time Packs.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1580277600,update_time1579762735